Privacy Policy for SuperHunt
Last Updated: March 9, 2026
Introduction
SuperHunt ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our Chrome extension.
Information We Collect
Information You Provide

Account Information: Email address and name when you sign up
Profile Data: Skills, experience level, and job preferences you enter during onboarding
Feedback: Reviews and comments you submit

Information Collected Automatically

Usage Data: Number of emails extracted, features used
Job Pipeline Data: Jobs you save, application status you set
Technical Data: Browser type, extension version

Information We Do NOT Collect

Your LinkedIn password or login credentials
Your LinkedIn messages or connections
Your browsing history outside of LinkedIn job pages
Any personal data from LinkedIn profiles you view

How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:

Provide and improve our email finding service
Track your job application pipeline
Calculate job match scores based on your skills
Send important service updates
Provide customer support

Data Storage and Security

All data is stored securely using Google Firebase
Data is encrypted in transit and at rest
We use industry-standard security measures
Your data is stored on servers located in the United States

Data Sharing
We do NOT:

Sell your personal data to third parties
Share your data with advertisers
Provide your information to data brokers

We may share data only:

With service providers who help operate our service (Firebase, Razorpay)
When required by law or legal process
To protect our rights or safety

Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access your personal data
Correct inaccurate data
Delete your account and data
Export your data
Opt out of marketing communications

To exercise these rights, contact us at support@superhunt.pro
Data Retention

We retain your data as long as your account is active
You can request deletion at any time
Deleted data is removed within 30 days

Third-Party Services
Our extension connects to:

LinkedIn: To read job posting information (publicly available data only)
Our API servers: To find and verify HR email addresses
Razorpay: To process payments (if you upgrade)

Children's Privacy
SuperHunt is not intended for users under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect data from children.
Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.
